official_title: A bill to amend title IV of the Agricultural Act of 1970 so as to extend the provisions of such title to the 1974 crop of winter wheat.

summary.text: Extends the provisions of Title IV of the Agricultural Act of 1970 concerning the crop of winter wheat through 1974, unless a new farm bill shall have been passed by Congress and signed by the President prior to July 1, 1973.
